\fBcitadel(1)\fP, \fBcitadel-whatsapp-connect(1)\fP, \fBcitadel-whatsapp-down(1)\fP, \fBcitadel-whatsapp-qr(1)\fP, \fBcitadel-whatsapp-status(1)\fP, \fBcitadel-whatsapp-up(1)\fP
